#: ../../source/unit/ac_measure.rst:3 e8fede9192c44b5c8964004bf14bf478
msgid "ACMeasure Unit"
msgstr "ACMeasure 单元"

#: ../../source/unit/ac_measure.rst:7 78321d74cf3644dfb3e311e886417d58
msgid ""
"C Measure Unit is a single-phase AC measurement module with isolation "
"capabilities. It utilizes the STM32+HLW8032 scheme to monitor high-"
"precision current, voltage, power, and other data in real time. The "
"module features a built-in AC isolation chip, B0505ST16-W5, and "
"communicates with the STM32 through the EL357 optocoupler isolation chip."
msgstr ""
"C Measure Unit 是一款具备隔离能力的单相 AC 测量模块。它采用 STM32+HLW8032 "
"方案，可实时监测高精度的电流、电压、功率等数据。该模块内置 AC 隔离芯片 B0505ST16-W5，并通过 EL357 光耦隔离芯片与 "
"STM32 通信。"

